(1, 1, 'A WordPress Commenter', 'wapuu@wordpress.example', 'https://wordpress.org/', '', '2018-10-04 22:53:06', '2018-10-04 22:53:06', 'Hi, this is a comment.\nTo get started with moderating, editing, and deleting comments, please visit the Comments screen in the dashboard.\nCommenter avatars come from <a href=\"https://gravatar.com\">Gravatar</a>.', 0, 'post-trashed', '', '', 0, 0),
(2, 9, 'Bob Sizoo', '', '', '', '2018-03-16 08:25:16', '2018-03-16 08:25:16', 'Nice strategy. I wish I\'d thought of it when I was teaching sixth grade, but this is definitely a habit that needs to be established in Kg or earlier. Keep up the good work on this blog.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(3, 9, 'Trish Wilkinson', '', '', '', '2018-03-16 08:47:57', '2018-03-16 08:47:57', 'Ha! Kids of all ages change their pencil grip—even adults. They just have to see how great it will be once they get used to the new grip and make the decision to learn the new habit.\n\nThis is also a great life-lesson—that we aren\'t stuck with something for the rest of our lives because we learned it when we were little. And kids love the tape!', 0, '1', '', '', 2, 0),
(4, 9, 'Trish', '', '', '', '2018-03-16 08:49:36', '2018-03-16 08:49:36', 'And thanks for the encouragement, Bob. I\'ve got some really cool posts coming up!', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(5, 11, 'Laura Sinton', '', '', '', '2018-05-04 05:23:08', '2018-05-04 05:23:08', 'This is stunningly effective. I am doing this with my granddaughter and am so impressed. Teaching her with play and fun makes her interested instead of feeling it’s a chore. Thank you!!', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0);
