 place for kids and parents by clicking the box at the bottom of this page to get exclusive tips.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To learn the surprising way Brain Stages came to be, click <a href=\"/blog/too-much-coincidence-not-to-be-part-of-the-cosmic-plan\">here.</a><br/>To find out more about the <em>Brain Stages</em> book, click <a href=\"/book.html\">here.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks for visiting!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>-Trish Wilkinson</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-0 is-cropped\"></ul>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->', 'About Brain Stages', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '22-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-10-10 20:29:38', '2018-10-10 20:29:38', '', 22, 'https://thebrainstages.com/2018/10/10/22-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
